"   <h1>",
"    REFERENCES",
"   </h1>",
"   <ol id=\"reference\">",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?30/29/31193/abstract/1\">",
"      Prentice A. Vitamin D deficiency: a global perspective. Nutr Rev 2008; 66:S153.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     Bouillon R. Vitamin D: from photosynthesis, metabolism and action to clinical applications. In: Endocrinology, Jameson JL, De Groot LJ (Eds), Saunders Elsevier, Philadelphia 2010. Vol 1, p.1089.",
